  "texts": [
    "Mu et al. [225] proposed a two-stage DL-based predictive beamforming algorithm for the ISAC-assisted V2X, where one roadside unit transmitted the dual-functional signal for predictive beamforming.",
    "Specifically, they first employed a DNN to fit the mapping from the measurements to the angles of vehicles, and then conducted the predictive beamforming according to the estimated angles.",
    "Following a similar scenario, Liu et al. [226] also studied the predictive beamforming for the ISAC-enabled V2X.",
    "They leveraged the CNN to extract the features of historic channels, which were fed into the RNN for beamforming prediction, bypassing the explicit channel tracking.",
    "Different from the aforementioned two-stage algorithms, Wang et al."
  ]
}